column16: Rusney Castillo grounds into a force out, shortstop Troy Tulowitzki to second baseman Ryan Goins.   Pablo Sandoval out at 2nd.
Hanley Ramirez grounds out, shortstop Troy Tulowitzki to first baseman Edwin Encarnacion.
Travis Shaw flies out to center fielder Kevin Pillar.
Dustin Pedroia doubles (2) on a line drive to right fielder Jose Bautista.   Mookie Betts scores.
Mookie Betts singles on a ground ball to center fielder Kevin Pillar.
Blake Swihart grounds out to first baseman Edwin Encarnacion.
Tim Beckham lines out to right fielder Jose Bautista.
Steven Souza Jr.   homers (3) on a fly ball to left center field.   Evan Longoria scores.    Desmond Jennings scores.
